data.description:
Move-in ready waterfront home! Beautifully upgraded 2-story Dream Finder home in sought-after Trailmark@World Golf Village. Flooded with natural light, this home features stone firepit...custom paver patio with LED lighting...soaring entryway...gourmet kitchen with quartz countertops, SS appliances, 42'' cabinets, glass backsplash, shiplap island and walk-in pantry! Luxurious master bedroom and bath. Spacious loft. New gutters, Light fixtures, fan, luxury vinyl plank +much more.  Spectacular finishing touches and fully fenced.    
Amenities include: Walking & Cycling Trails, Kayak Launch & Winding Waterways. Resort Style Pool, Fitness Center, Tennis Courts and Playground+++ Hurry--it will sell fast!
